@startuml 01_component_architecture
!theme plain
skinparam componentStyle uml2

package "B1 Edge Detection Layer" {
    component "CameraStream\n(Background Thread)" as Cam
    component "TrafficDetector\n(YOLOv8)" as Det
    component "SpeedCalculator\n(Bounding Box History)" as Spd
    component "LaneEnricher\n(Spatial Mapping)" as Lane
    component "TrafficKafkaProducer\n(Kafka Egress)" as Prod
    component "OfflineBuffer\n(SQLite Disk)" as Buf
    component "FastAPI Server\n(API, Metrics/Health)" as API
}

database "Camera Feed (RTSP/File)" as Feed
cloud "Kafka Broker / B2" as Kafka

Feed --> Cam : Video Frames
Cam -right-> Det : get_frame()
Det --> Spd : Tracking IDs & BBoxes
Det --> Lane : Centroids
Spd --> Prod : Speed (km/h)
Lane --> Prod : Lane IDs
Prod -right-> Kafka : JSON Telemetry
Prod <--> Buf : Store/Replay on network drop

API ..> Det : Read metrics (e.g., latency)
API ..> Cam : Read snapshots

@enduml